<br>
However..in RL im a firefighter/paramedic for the past 6 years and 2 years before that on an ambulance. (hence why at age 30 i can have a lvl 176 MA lol..time off rules).<br>
<br>
What I want to say is this: as alot (not all) of the people who play mmrpgs are younger and emotions/hormones etc are crazy at a younger age...suicide is NEVER EVER EVER NEVER the answer. <br>
<br>
I can read the posts here..everyone seems stable lol.  Im not a psychologist by any means..but maybe you KNOW someone who isnt...maybe you are the kid who is shunned in school..know someone like that etc...<br>
<br>
DO something about it. please. make a new friend. help someone out. get away from the computer for a while. <br>
<br>
Its way way to final.<br>
<br>
There is nothing worse then the tones going off at the station..for a possible suicide. Getting to someones house and finding a 19 y/o male who hung himself in the garage. neck 6 inches longer, tongue black, pissed/shit himself, eyes bugged out.  <br>
<br>
Or going to a 13 y/o house who decided to use a gun to the roof of his mouth...its just like the movies...we have all seen &quot;Full Metal Jacket&quot;.  <br>
<br>
They are dead. they will never have kids, they will never go to another concert, they will never see how life plays out.<br>
<br>
The worst part is who finds them...its not the kids at school they are mad it..its the parents. The anguish I have seen on suicide calls is just insane. I actually cried at the hanging...seeing the Mom..who found her son in the garage with motorcycle tie downs around his neck.  <br>
<br>
Its the families who suffer. the friends. the people at school who didnt even know him/her.<br>
<br>
I have been an many suicides...and attempt suicides..and just cries for help. It is never the answer. EVER. <br>
<br>
ok..sorry about my post. but some things just hit home. <br>
<br>
now go have fun and drink a beer for god's sake lol.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub83.ezboard.com/uautumndawnfire.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Autumn Dawnfire</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.melanierawn.com/images/bunnie.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Peking Duck</span><br>  Posts: 181<br> <font color=#660000>(4/4/02 8:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub83.ezboard.com/fthepunchingbag74708frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1851.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Suicide....by a person close to it...</span><hr size=1> Mad prob's from an ex'cop.<br>
