<br>
It's like a band-aid. My death my cause some pain for a few people, but it passes. They get on with their lives. <br>
<br>
No matter what you do (in that situation) someone's going to be in pain. Either the people who care about you and are hurt by your death. Or you yourself are hurt by having to continue to live a life you don't want. <br>
